*[[버드나무]] (''beodeu-namu'') (''literally, "willow tree"'') cf. German '''[[Weidenbaum]]'''
*버들나모 (''beodeul-namo'') (''obsolete; literally, "willow tree"'') 
*유 ([[柳]], ''yu'') 
*양 ([[楊]], ''yang'') 

